Package: poptrend
Title: Estimate Smooth and Linear Trends from Population Count Survey Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Jonas", "Knape", email = "jonas.knape@slu.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions to estimate and plot smooth or linear population trends, or population indices, 
    from animal or plant count survey data.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Imports:
    mgcv (>= 1.7.0),
    stats,
    graphics
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
URL: https://github.com/jknape/poptrend
BugReports: https://github.com/jknape/poptrend/issues
